{"tid":1071813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"攝取1克蛋白質係配磅定係kg？？","createTime":"2019-03-21T15:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T15:38:44.000Z","uid":210755,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"90973f1acd8b00ac694078cd1087ab31c9de2f7c","tid":1071813,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:03:55.000Z","msg":"廿幾萬Follower <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w5rSQhH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw5rSQhH.jpg&h=a27240bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾千Follower <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ea60eKt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fea60eKt.jpg&h=1ec8433b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到廣告哩兩個Page 都話每磅體種攝取1克蛋白質, 健身攝取1.5~2克<br />\n<br />\n假設183cm, 215磅, 23%體脂<br />\n如果要減至10%體脂, 即係要減27.95磅(13%)多餘脂肪<br />\n即係宜家嘅Muscle mass係o係187磅<br />\n<br />\n有兩個問題<br />\n-每克蛋白質攝取量 係計你體重 定係muscle  mass <br />\n(eg.同樣200磅：1個肌肉仔 / 1個大肥鳩) <br />\n-每克蛋白質配磅定kg<br />\n(覺得用磅好似唔合理) <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n健身, 215磅x2克蛋白質 = 430克<br />\n假設：<br />\n健身前後飲蛋白奶 25g+25g= 50g<br />\n早餐 兩塊大雞排肉 25g+25g=50g<br />\n午餐&amp; 晚餐 同上 50+50g<br />\n總共：200g 另加主食嘅蛋白質+50g(應該食唔到咁多主食) <br />\n咁樣先250g, 遠遠都唔夠每磅2克(430克)"},{"pid":"0678d08ab9e2c2053cface6d35e1a777112c8f4c","tid":1071813,"uid":142359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9b6a91c816d0d12a6d4d50e1f8e27354fd43bd","tid":1071813,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:06:38.000Z","msg":"即使計Muscle mass 187磅x 2克 =374克蛋白質 都係遠遠唔夠"},{"pid":"b87a41ec63c7e85dc368c56a999b53fc8624ea4d","tid":1071813,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:10:48.000Z","msg":"其實仲見好多Post 都拋幾粒字出黎, 每磅體重攝取1克蛋白質, 有重訓就1.5-2克<br />\n就話有重訓 唔夠 需要大量蛋白質合成 修補,講d似是而非嘅野, 又大把人like 比心心, 無人覺得唔合理？"},{"pid":"1cc0605f3393eaec23cf71d117af274f637c939a","tid":1071813,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a3403071660fa95c516100b920fe60e0767361","tid":1071813,"uid":143474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"per kg<br />\n<br />\n利申 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea8c3477d76f185559aad5ca7c2cbb21b094884","tid":1071813,"uid":143474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"btw 你冇計 bone mass"}]}